{"tid":1133342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人母】蒼井空順利誕孖仔","createTime":"2019-05-01T03:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T04:30:50.000Z","uid":106957,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"44b701dd8d556042e8605a82f7ed4a680b114e41","tid":1133342,"uid":106957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T03:46:51.000Z","msg":"現年35歲的日本前AV女優蒼井空，去年與DJ NON拉埋天窗，更成功克服不孕，陀有孖胎的她昨晚趁平成最後一日，以網上直播跟全亞洲網民及Fans分享生仔喜悅。<br />\n<br />\n今晨10時蒼井空的微博上，更新了一段文字：「不好意思大家。我是老公，她說她馬上生孩子去。會加油的。」並附上蒼井空於病床上揮手的圖片。<br />\n<br />\n大約1小時後，蒼井空微博再有更新，表示：「生了！兩個寶貝2.200公斤和2.500公斤，感謝老婆，辛苦了！我們一家快樂的生活吧！」<br />\n<br />\nlink：<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190501&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=59550381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190501%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D59550381&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEBZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=58ad0f18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190501%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D59550381&h=4c88c482\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190501&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=59550381</a><br />\n<br />\n一定好多奶汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小朋友一定好健康"},{"pid":"26343542fcac77a54455110cd51809013dd313c7","tid":1133342,"uid":72009,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T03:47:59.000Z","msg":"希望佢地Ｄ同學將來唔知佢老母係那個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52ce0cc531a4faa526000478a17ea37f3543f0b","tid":1133342,"uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T03:48:40.000Z","msg":"一人一邊，老公唯有飲西水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a2f3565a2bf4cb32733a1e98518d790ede2330","tid":1133342,"uid":66725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T03:52:10.000Z","msg":"一睇以為